<C>__{thatcher}
<D>__{mr goodman, now, is the foremost pigeon fancier in all the southern counties. kent champion two years running. i swear he can give you any beak or plumage in four generations. head and tail in five.}
<C>__{darwin}
<D>__{how do you do it?}
<C>__{gooodman}
<D>__{by breeding cousin with cousin. i find it the fastest way to alter the strain provided you do not weaken it in other ways.}
